import { NavList } from '@primer/react'
import {
    GitPullRequestIcon,
    HomeIcon,
    IssueOpenedIcon,
} from '@primer/octicons-react'

export function SideNav() {
    return (
        <NavList
            sx={{
                width: '300px',
                bg: 'red',
                height: '100vh',
            }}
        >
            <NavList.Item href="/" aria-current="page">
                <NavList.LeadingVisual>
                    <HomeIcon />
                </NavList.LeadingVisual>
                Dashboard
            </NavList.Item>
            <NavList.Item href="/pulls">
                <NavList.LeadingVisual>
                    <GitPullRequestIcon />
                </NavList.LeadingVisual>
                Pull requests
            </NavList.Item>
            <NavList.Item href="/issues">
                <NavList.LeadingVisual>
                    <IssueOpenedIcon />
                </NavList.LeadingVisual>
                Issues
            </NavList.Item>
        </NavList>
    )
}
